dct_description_sm: Map shows railways, oil pipelines, wells, and cemeteries of different religions. Important buildings are listed and located. Inset: Bizerte and Ferryville. Scale 1:200,000. "7/42/GSGS." "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 110139. 1942. 2-43." "Approximate mean declination 1942. Annual magnetic change 7ʹ decrease for center of sheet."
